summary: This Cozy house is the perfect house for anyone who loves a beautiful get away. As you stand outside of the house, you can almost smell the nature.
descriptionHtml:
This Cozy house is the perfect house for anyone who loves a beautiful get away. As you stand outside of the house, you can almost smell the nature.

There was a huge problem in Skyrim, there is no house in Falkreath! I had to fix this, so I made a mod that adds a beautiful house just on top of the hill next to Falkreath. 

==============
Hey Guys, if you guys like this mod, please endorse, or show show some love in the Comments. 
If you feel like you want to donate, or want more information on some mods, head to my Tumblr!

267mods.tumblr.com
=================
The house is located right on top of the hill next to Falkreath. You can also see where it is in pictures.
================
Installation:

Just drop the .esp into your Data sub-folder within the Skyrim folder.
Same way you install any other mod.

PS. This mod will also be in the workshop, for those who like that better.
===============
1.1v

The shield racks don\'t work, please stay tuned on when I get those working, but the mannequins and the weapons racks all work perfectly! Everything else works great!.

- Fully Nav Meshed
- Map Marker
==============
Contact:
If you would like to email me for any questions, please feel free to do so at <> bill267mods@gmail.com <> or follow me on twitter <> @Bill267mods <>  or my blog <> 267mods.tumblr.com
